Achievements.Name: Top Agent
Achievements.Description: Bonus for completing the game on Normal difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Heroic Agent
Achievements.Description: Bonus for completing the game on Experienced difficulty.

Achievements.Name: Legendary Agent
Achievements.Description: Bonus for completing the game on Hardcore difficulty.

Achievements.Name: First Taste of Chaos
Achievements.Description: Cause chaos for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Gravity is a Bitch!
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies by using the grappling hook and making them fall to their death.

Achievements.Name: Follow Me!
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemies by dragging them behind a vehicle with the grappling hook.

Achievements.Name: Hang 'em High!
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies while they're suspended in the air with the grappling hook.

Achievements.Name: Wrecking Ball
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemies by smashing them with an object tethered to your vehicle with the grappling hook.

Achievements.Name: Piata Party
Achievements.Description: Kill 5 enemies with the melee attack while they're suspended with the grappling hook.

Achievements.Name: Juggler
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies while they're in mid air.

Achievements.Name: Road Rage
Achievements.Description: Kill 30 enemies by mowing them down with vehicles.

Achievements.Name: Invincible Warrior
Achievements.Description: Kill 50 enemies in a row with inventory weapons without losing health.

Achievements.Name: Please Step Out of the Vehicle
Halfway there
Achievements.Description: Reach 50% completion in the normal mode or mercenary mode.

Achievements.Name: Parachute Climber
Achievements.Description: Open the parachute and then land on foot 300 meters above the starting height.

Achievements.Name: Bridge Limbo
Achievements.Description: Fly an airplane under 30 unique bridges in Panau.

Achievements.Name: Stunt Flyer
Achievements.Description: Fly an airplane close to the ground for 30 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Perfectionist
Achievements.Description: Reach 75% completion in the normal mode or mercenary mode.

Achievements.Name: Top of the World
Achievements.Description: Stand on foot on the highest point of Panau
